name: Rebirth of the Gorgon
description:
The Gorgon returns from the shadows — a symbol of power, awakening, and truth.
The mantle cloaks old skin; her gaze pierces the veil.
This is no ritual of vengeance — but remembrance.
The return of the Archetype, the Woman who turns fear into freedom.
You don’t just look at the Gorgon — she sees into you. #SpiritGorgons #Rebirth #GorgonNFT #DigitalMyth #ArchetypeAwakening #MysticArt #FemininePower #CryptoMyth #Metamorphosis
